Brian Young & Janet Gamache of WTDI are the Event Coordinating team of the Longwood Pirate Seafood Festival and the Longwood Arts & Crafts Festival.
If you would like information about other events that WTDI coordinates, you can go to the website
FestivalsWithJanet.com
Contact them directly at
FestivalswithJanet@gmail.com
or call 352-217-8390
This website was designed to help visitors and vendors navigate through information about the Longwood Pirate Seafood Festival and the Longwood Arts and Crafts Festival and is not affiliated with the City of Longwood.
CLICK HERE
to visit the official City of Longwood website.
